{
  "stem": "7358.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So as a matter of fact, the next morning when my aunt came to bring me something to eat in the morning, when she opened the door-- she left the place dry.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when she opened the door and she walked down, she got halfway into the water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was that much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after that, they took me-- they made a decision-- my uncle made a decision to go into another location altogether.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Leave this area because he thought it was a well known to the Germans that Jews are hiding there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, they took me, and my cousin dragged me on his back, perhaps 10 miles distance, maybe longer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't even know how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we came to another location.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the one cousin, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came to another location, and they made a temporary hut underground because that was supposed to be just for the summer.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And little by little, my feet got slightly better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From branches, they made me like crutches, and I was able to begin to walk around a little bit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took big shoes, and they put in cotton and cloth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was able to sort of move around a little bit, to get up, and get off my bed, and walk around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We stayed there for about, perhaps six months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With my uncle, there was always other people that wanted to be near him because they felt safe next to him, because he had a rifle, and his son had a rifle.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And already, the farmers had great respect for him because they were afraid of him, some of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So anyone that was associated with my uncle at that point was-- felt reasonably safe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was always other people.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
